{"tid":1517893,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(又贏!)美國檢察機構正就華為涉嫌竊取知識產權　展開新調查","createTime":"2019-08-30T05:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T05:15:10.000Z","uid":50457,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96e42a817b44cecdf7f8336cdbc00edbadf45725","tid":1517893,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"美國《華爾街日報》引述消息人士報道，美國檢察機構正就中國電信商華為涉嫌竊取知識產權，進行新一輪的調查。報道表示，有關調查包括指華為在過去數年，從個人與企業竊取技術，並從競爭對手挖角員工。<br />\n<br />\n報道表示，美國政府最新針對華為的調查方向，並不包括今年較早前在起訴書中所指控華為的商業行為。華為和美國司法部至今未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n在今年1月，美國司法部指控華為及高層孟晚舟合謀違反美國對伊朗的制裁，通過華為試圖隱瞞一家子公司與伊朗做生意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477666-20190830.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477666-20190830.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8q0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=32df1544\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477666-20190830.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aa6dabd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477666-20190830.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3c0ecb4c340e8c1e9479e80fd7ebd4bca2c0035e","tid":1517893,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8q0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=40f90cc3\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8q0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=29